  🎯 SPA Front-End: ASCII Wireframes for EPC Accounting System

  ★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────
  Domain Understanding: This system serves Indonesian electrical panel manufacturers and solar EPC contractors. Key insight: EPC businesses have a unique flow where a single project touches Sales → Engineering → Procurement → Production → Finance. The UI must support this cross-functional journey while keeping each role's view focused.
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

  ---
  PHASE 1: EXECUTIVE OVERVIEW (Owner/Management)

  The owner's primary concern: "How is my money?" and "Are projects profitable?"

